        Creates a new instance of GetResult.
        Parameters:
        numOfResults - Number of documents returned by the search server instance.
        results - A list of results parsed to Document.
        getQuery - The fulltext query executed to retrieve this set of results.
        docFactory - document factory holding the schema configuration of documents to parse the results to.
